description: Today there are over 10 million Medicare-Medicaid enrollees in the United States.To provide a greater understanding of the Medicare-Medicaid enrollee population, the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services (CMS) has put together state profiles that examine the demographic characteristics, utilization, condition prevalence, and spending patterns of Medicare-Medicaid enrollees and the programs that serve them in each state.
title: Medicare-Medicaid Enrollee Profiles (State and National)
